                      | Little Greta, international 
                      a(href="http://www.littlegreta.co.uk/#about-us-section", target="_blank") full-service agency, with specialities in digital media, design and multimedia
                      | , is proud to announce the opening of a new German office, part of its strategy to develop a&nbsp;global offer.
                    p.t-indent
                      i &ldquo;In addition to the UK, which is our core market, recently we&#8217;ve been building our profile in Austria and Germany. We want to increase our activity in these two countries and opening an office demonstrates our intentions. We see this as one of Europe&#8217;s key markets, with many new opportunities for Little Greta,&rdquo;
