                tr
                  td.l-text-column.l-content--narrow
                    p While in Germany we might be the new kids on the block, in the UK we&#8217;re now well established in the market and growing our portfolio. Our UK business development is led by Owen Morgan.
                    p.t-indent
                      i &ldquo;We&#8217;re proud to be working with well-known international partners like Partners Andrews Aldridge of the Engine Group and NIIT Technologies,&rdquo;
                      |  he says. To see more of our work 
                      a(href="http://www.littlegreta.co.uk/#portfolio-section", target="_blank") visit our portfolio
                      | .
                tr
                  td.l-content
                    q.o-quote In the first 6 months of 2014, we&#8217;ve delivered over 40 projects, mostly web design, animation, graphic design and copywriting.
                tr
                  td.l-content--narrow.l-right.l-spaced--top
                    span.o-quote__author &mdash; Owen Morgan, UK Business Development Manager
                tr
                  td.l-text-column.l-content--narrow
