                      i &ldquo;Over the last 2 years we&#8217;ve grown our UK business rather organically. In 2015 we&#8217;d like to boost it significantly through finding the right investment. We&#8217;re keen to talk to interested parties who can see the potential in what we are trying to achieve; partners whose experience can teach as to perform better as well,&rdquo;
